//////////////////////////////
//Item Types and Definitions//
//////////////////////////////
ITYPE_1: POTION
ITYPE_2: KEY_ITEM
ITYPE_3: WEAPON
ITYPE_4: MISC_ITEM

///////////////////////////////
//Spell Types and Definitions//
///////////////////////////////
STYPE_1: DIRECTDMG
STYPE_2: AOEDMG
STYPE_3: HEALING

Direct Damaging spells will only have an impact on the enemy which it is directed to

Area of Effect spells will have 'Splash' damage, where it can hit more than one enemy

Healing spells will heal the user